多位演员和名流在片中以真实身份出镜，其中包括[[托比·马奎尔|托比·马奎尔]]、[[提拉·班克斯|提拉·班克斯]]、[[玛丽娅·曼努诺斯|玛丽娅·曼努诺斯]]（{{lang|en|Maria Menounos}}）、[[马丁·劳伦斯|马丁·劳伦斯]]、[[杰森·贝特曼|杰森·贝特曼]]、[[兰斯·巴斯|兰斯·巴斯]]、[[詹妮弗·洛芙·休伊特|詹妮弗·洛芙·休伊特]]、[[艾丽西亚·希尔维斯通|艾丽西亚·希尔维斯通]]和[[强·沃特|强·沃特]]。另外，[[克里斯蒂娜·泰勒_(演員)|克里斯蒂娜·泰勒]]（{{lang|en|Christine Taylor}}，她还是本·斯蒂勒的夫人）、[[米妮·安顿|米妮·安顿]]（{{lang|en|Mini Anden}}）、[[安东尼·雷维瓦|安东尼·雷维瓦]]（{{lang|en|Anthony Ruivivar}}）、蕾切尔·艾弗里（{{lang|en|Rachel Avery}}）和[[伊薇特·尼科尔·布朗|伊薇特·尼科尔·布朗]]（{{lang|en|Yvette Nicole Brown}}）在片中出演了小角色。编剧贾斯汀·塞洛克斯也在电影中露了两次面，一次是[[UH-1直升机|UH-1直升机]]上的机枪手，另一次则是电影《[[名模大間諜|名模大間諜]]》删除镜头中的[[唱片骑师|唱片骑师]]。<ref name="DVDCommJustin">{{cite video | title = Tropic Thunder-(Filmmaker Commentary by Ben Stiller, Justin Theroux, Stuart Cornfeld, Jeff Man, John Toll, and Greg Hayden) | medium = Blu-ray Disc | publisher = DreamWorks | time = 5:36 | date = 2008-11-18}}</ref><ref name="DVDCommJustinDJ">{{cite video | title = Tropic Thunder-(Filmmaker Commentary by Ben Stiller, Justin Theroux, Stuart Cornfeld, Jeff Man, John Toll, and Greg Hayden) | medium = Blu-ray Disc | publisher = DreamWorks | time = 23:54 | date = 2008-11-18}}</ref>

== 制作 ==
=== 剧本 ===
{{quote box|width=30em|quote=“……我觉得这部电影有自己的基调。其中有讽刺的元素，但我并不认为影片就局限于此。其中也有戏仿的元素，但我显然也不认为影片就只是这些。我希望电影有自己的基调，我们表现了许多熟悉的内容。”|source=针对称本片属[[戲仿|恶搞]]之作的评论，斯蒂勒这样回应。<ref name="PushBoundaries">{{cite news|last=Portman |first=Jamie |title=Stiller pushes boundaries with war-film farce |work=The Gazette |publisher=Canwest News Service |date=2008-08-06 |accessdate=2014-11-06 |deadurl=yes |url=http://www.canada.com/montrealgazette/news/arts/story.html?id=321a81c3-ae46-4299-b224-2ffe32baad27 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121108160544/http://www.canada.com/montrealgazette/news/arts/story.html?id=321a81c3-ae46-4299-b224-2ffe32baad27 |archivedate=2012-11-08 }}</ref>}}
斯蒂勒曾在《[[太阳帝国_(电影)|太阳帝国]]》中出演过一个小角色，他在该片拍摄期间构想出《热带惊雷》的大致框架<ref name="ew">{{cite news|last=Vary |first=Adam B. |title=First Look: 'Tropic Thunder' |work=Entertainment Weekly |date=2008-03-03 |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20182058,00.html |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006090731/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0%2C%2C20182058%2C00.html |archivedate=2014-10-06 |accessdate=2014-10-06 }}</ref>。他知道有些演员在为战争电影角色做准备而参加新兵训练营后会变得有些“妄自尊大”、“自以为是”，觉得自己就真是当过兵的人了，斯蒂勒想拍一部有关这类演员的电影<ref name="FakeBoot">{{cite news | last = Wynter | first = Kareen | title = 'Tropic Thunder' pushes envelope and then some | publisher = CNN | date = 2008-08-11 | url = http://edition.cnn.com/2008/SHOWBIZ/Movies/08/11/tropic.thunder/index.html | accessdate = 2011-01-31 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2011-01-31 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110131211933/http://edition.cnn.com/2008/SHOWBIZ/Movies/08/11/tropic.thunder/index.html}}</ref><ref name="HollySpo">{{cite news | last = Tourtellotte | first = Bob | title = Hollywood, an easy target for "Tropic Thunder" jokes | publisher = Reuters | date = 2008-08-11 | accessdate = 2013-06-30 | deadurl = yes | url = http://blogs.reuters.com/fanfare/2008/08/11/hollywood-an-easy-target-for-tropic-thunder-jokes/ | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130630185919/http://blogs.reuters.com/fanfare/2008/08/11/hollywood-an-easy-target-for-tropic-thunder-jokes/ | archivedate = 2013-06-30}}</ref>。据编剧塞洛克斯透露，剧本起初讲述的是多位演员前去参加模拟新兵训练营，但回来时已经患上了[[创伤后心理压力紧张症候群|创伤后心理压力紧张综合症]]<ref name="DVDCommPTSD">{{cite video | title = Tropic Thunder-(Before the Thunder) | medium = Blu-ray Disc | publisher = DreamWorks | time = 1:25 | date = 2008-11-18}}</ref>。最终完成的剧本讽刺了多部越战电影，如《[[现代启示录|现代启示录]]》、《[[野战排_(电影)|野战排]]》、《[[全金属外壳|全金属外壳]]》、《[[血肉战场|血肉战场]]》和《[[猎鹿人|猎鹿人]]》<ref name="TelegraphReviewDeer">{{cite news | last = Sandhu | first = Sukhdev | title = Film review: Tropic Thunder | publisher = Telegraph.co.uk | date = 2008-09-19 | accessdate = 2014-11-07 | archivedate = 2013-02-24 | location = London | url = http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/film/filmreviews/3560875/Film-review-Tropic-Thunder.html | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130224085137/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/film/filmreviews/3560875/Film-review-Tropic-Thunder.html}}</ref><ref name="MitchellFilms">{{cite news |last=Mitchell |first=Peter |title=Robert Downey Jr. talks 'Tropic Thunder' |work=The New Zealand Herald |date=2008-08-22 |accessdate=2014-11-07 |url=http://www.nzherald.co.nz/movies/news/article.cfm?c_id=200&objectid=10528050 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5u4Yyzwgp?url=http://www.nzherald.co.nz/movies/news/article.cfm?c_id=200 |archivedate=2010-11-07 }}</ref>。塞洛克斯指出，由于明星网站和好莱坞新闻的影响，观众对好莱坞内部运作有了更多的认识，这也降低了本片剧本创作的难度<ref name="HollySpo" />。一些剧本中没有的台词则是演员在片场即兴发挥的产物<ref name="DVDCommImprovise">{{cite video | title = Tropic Thunder-(Cast Commentary by Ben Stiller, Jack Black, and Robert Downey Jr.) | medium = Blu-ray Disc | publisher = DreamWorks | date = 2008-11-18}}</ref>。

=== 演员选择 ===
{{double image|right|Robert Downey Jr. 2011 AA.jpg|125|DowneyKirkLazarusTTCostume.jpg|170|[[小罗伯特·唐尼|小罗伯特·唐尼]]（左）出演柯克·拉扎勒斯（右）时需要化妆两小时}}
伊坦·柯亨设计柯克·拉扎勒斯一角是旨在讽刺一些方法演员费九牛二虎之力诠释角色的做法<ref name="ew" /><ref name="WarGamesDN">{{cite news | last = Whipp | first = Glenn | title = War Games: It was jungle fever of a different kind for ''Tropic Thunder'' troops | accessdate = 2014-11-07 | deadurl = no | work = Daily News of Los Angeles | url = http://www.thefreelibrary.com/WAR+GAMES+IT+WAS+JUNGLE+FEVER+OF+A+DIFFERENT+KIND+FOR+'TROPIC...-a0182769128 | archivedate = 2011-06-15 | date = 2008-08-10 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110615035505/http://goliath.ecnext.com/coms2/gi_0199-8220317/WAR-GAMES-IT-WAS-JUNGLE.html}}</ref>。斯蒂勒联系唐尼时，后者正在[[夏威夷州|夏威夷州]]度假<ref name="DowneyHawaii">{{cite news | last = Saval | first = Malina | title = Robert Downey Jr., 'Tropic Thunder' | work = Variety | date = 2008-12-05 | accessdate = 2014-11-07 | url = http://variety.com/2008/film/awards/robert-downey-jr-tropic-thunder-1117996908/ | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141107123353/http://variety.com/2008/film/awards/robert-downey-jr-tropic-thunder-1117996908/ | archivedate = 2014-11-07}}</ref>。唐尼在接受{{lang|en|[[CBS_(电视网)|CBS]]}}电视台《[[早间秀|早间秀]]》节目采访表示，自己当时的第一反应是：“这真是我听过最愚蠢的点子！”而斯蒂勒的回应则是：“就是嘛——这真太棒了！”<ref name="CBS">{{cite video | url = https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-EU_vi6QgeY | title = Robert Downey Jr. on 'Thunder' | publisher = CBS | date = 2008-08-18 | accessdate = 2010-11-07 | archive-date = 2013-08-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130802065746/http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-EU_vi6QgeY | dead-url = no }}</ref>。唐尼还在另一次采访中表示，自己虽然同意接演，但对应该如何表现这个人物却一点思路都没有，最终他决定采用[[非洲裔美国人白话英语|摇摆式]]说话风格，并且嗓音低沉而沙哑，接下来他在与斯蒂勒通电话时用这样的声音试镜，导演马上就拍板决定采纳这一风格<ref name="WonderBoysAlley" />。唐尼表示，自己诠释这个角色时是以[[罗素·克劳|罗素·克劳]]、[[柯林·法瑞尔|柯林·法瑞尔]]和[[丹尼尔·戴-刘易斯|丹尼尔·戴-刘易斯]]三位男演员为原型<ref name="DowneyCharacters">{{cite news|last=Douglas |first=Edward |title=Ben Stiller Feels the Tropic Thunder |publisher=[http://www.comingsoon.net/ ComingSoon.net] |date=2008-03-17 |deadurl=yes |url=http://www.comingsoon.net/news/showestnews.php?id=42984 |accessdate=2014-11-07 |archivedate=2012-09-29 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120929211712/http://www.comingsoon.net/news/showestnews.php?id=42984 }}</ref>。柯克·拉扎勒斯在起初的剧本中是[[爱尔兰人|爱尔兰人]]，但唐尼表示，如果角色是澳大利亚人，他可以更好地即兴发挥，他曾在《[[天生杀人狂|天生杀人狂]]》中出演过类似的古怪人物，并且那也是个澳大利亚人，于是拉扎勒斯也就改写成了澳大利亚人<ref name="AustMate">{{cite news | last = Itzkoff | first = Dave | title = Spoof Within a Movie Within a Movie Within ... | work = The New York Times | date = 2008-08-10 | url = http://www.nytimes.com/2008/08/10/movies/10dave.html?_r=1&ref=arts | publisher = The New York Times Company | accessdate = 2014-11-07 | archivedate = 2014-11-07 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141107125243/http://www.nytimes.com/2008/08/10/movies/10dave.html?_r=2&ref=arts&}}</ref>。唐尼在拍摄间隙、甚至离开片场时仍然保持在入戏状态，剧本中也加入了相应内容由他的角色表演<ref name="PlayingWar">{{cite news | last = Ordoña | first = Michael | title = Playing war gets serious in 'Thunder' | work = San Francisco Chronicle | archivedate = 2014-10-29 | accessdate = 2014-11-07 | deadurl = no | date = 2008-08-10 | url = http://www.sfgate.com/entertainment/article/Playing-war-gets-serious-in-Thunder-3200343.php | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141029094925/http://www.sfgate.com/entertainment/article/Playing-war-gets-serious-in-Thunder-3200343.php}}</ref>。唐尼的化妆过程需要耗费一个半到两小时的时间<ref name="DVDCommMakeup">{{cite video | title = Tropic Thunder-(Cast of Tropic Thunder-Downey Jr.) | medium = Blu-ray Disc | publisher = DreamWorks | time = 2:33 | date = 2008-11-11}}</ref><ref name="DowneyEWMakeup">{{cite journal | last = Svetkey | first = Benjamin | title = Robert Downey Jr.: Tropic Thunder | journal = Entertainment Weekly | page = 60 | issue = 1032 | date = 2009-01-30}}</ref>，对此他表示：“一名化妆师从我脸的这一边开始，另一名则在另一边开始，然后他们会在中间会师”<ref name="DowneyEWMakeup" />。

唐尼知道，自己的角色有可能会引发争议：“归根究底，这里探讨的是你对角色到底有多投入。如果我觉得这在道德上有些站不住脚，或是很容易让人误以为我只不过是（《[[灵魂男人|灵魂男人]]》中的）[[C·托马斯·豪威尔|C·托马斯·豪威尔]]的话，我会直接就待在家里”<ref name="ew" />。[[布兰登·T·杰克逊|布兰登·T·杰克逊]]表示：“我刚看到剧本的时候就想着：什么情况？[[扮演黑人|扮演黑人]]？但当我看到他，就那么变成一个黑人……这样的表演真是太棒了。在片场的时候情况很怪异，因为他一直都沉浸在自己的角色里。他是方法演员”<ref name="PeopleJacksonQ">{{cite news|last=McGee |first=Tiffany |title=Costar Praises Robert Downey Jr. for Race-Bending Role |work=People |date=2008-07-18 |accessdate=2014-11-07 |deadurl=no |url=http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20213599,00.html |archivedate=2014-01-22 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140122222605/http://www.people.com/people/article/0%2C%2C20213599%2C00.html }}</ref>。对于身为白人演员的唐尼却来扮演黑人，斯蒂勒表示：“从电影的背景上来说，他是在扮演一名白人演员，而这位方法演员又非常投入地在出演一个黑人。对于观众们来说，他们看到的就是一部恶搞演员、并且讲述这些演员是何等认真地对待自己角色的电影”<ref name="StillInterEmpire">{{cite news|last=Horkins |first=Tony |title=Exclusive: Stiller Talks Tropic Thunder |work=Empire |date=2008-03-18 |url=http://www.empireonline.com/news/story.asp?NID=22188 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130614132312/http://www.empireonline.com/news/story.asp?NID=22188 |archivedate=2013-06-14 |accessdate=2014-11-07 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。斯蒂勒安排多位黑人新闻工作者和[[美国全国有色人种协进会|美国全国有色人种协进会]]预先看过本片，他们对这个角色有着良好的迴响<ref name="PlayingWar" />。

{{double image|right|TomCruiseDec08MTV cropped.jpg|145|TomCruiseLesGrossmanTTCostume.jpg|175|[[汤姆·克鲁斯|汤姆·克鲁斯]]（左）和他扮演的莱斯·格罗斯曼（右）。为了演好这个人物，他穿上了增肥装，还带有更粗壮的假手，以及化妆成秃头的頭套。}}
汤姆·克鲁斯起初只是客串出演斯蒂勒角色的经纪人里克·佩克，但在他的提议下，片中新增了制片公司总裁一角。莱斯·格罗斯曼由斯蒂勒和克鲁斯共同创作，是位中年商人。出演这一人物时，克鲁斯需要穿上增肥装，并装上塑料制成、看上去更粗壮的假手，以及化妆成秃头的頭套<ref name="TrailerEddie" /><ref name="AustMate" />。正是克鲁斯提议让人物的手看上去更大，并在片尾随着[[佛罗·里达|佛罗·里达]]的歌曲“{{lang|en|[[Low_(佛罗·里达歌曲)|Low]]}}”起舞<ref name="CruiseHandLow">{{cite web | title = Friday Night with Jonathan Ross: Series 16: Episode 1 | publisher = BBC iPlayer | date = 2009-01-23 | url = http://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b00fm6wz | accessdate = 2014-11-07 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130809225244/http://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b00fm6wz | archivedate = 2013-08-09}}</ref>。斯蒂勒打算把克鲁斯的角色保密，直到电影上映时再由观众自己去发现；此外，[[派拉蒙电影|派拉蒙电影]]也拒绝把克鲁斯的角色形象照片向媒体公布<ref name="cieply">{{cite news | last = Cieply | first = Michael | accessdate = 2014-11-07 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141107140854/http://www.nytimes.com/2008/04/03/movies/03crui.html?ref=movies&_r=0 | url = http://www.nytimes.com/2008/04/03/movies/03crui.html?ref=movies&_r=0 | title = Tom Cruise, in Bit Role, Nips Studio's Top Gun | work = The New York Times | date = 2008-04-03 | publisher = The New York Times Company | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-11-07}}</ref>。2007年12月，克鲁斯秃顶并且身穿增肥装的照片出现在《内部版本》（{{lang|en|''Inside Edition''}}）[[电视节目|节目]]和[[互联网|互联网]]上<ref name="FatSuitTom">{{cite news | last = Hazlett | first = Courtney | url = http://www.today.com/id/21870944 | title = Tom Cruise's fat-suit fracas | publisher = NBCNEWS.com | date = 2007-11-18 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130624225347/http://www.today.com/id/21870944 | archivedate = 2013-06-24 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2014-11-07 | work = msnbc.com}}</ref><ref name="PeopleCameo">{{cite news|last=Silverman |first=Stephen M. |url=http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20188076,00.html |title=Revealed: More Details on Tom Cruise's Cameo in Tropic Thunder |work=People |date=2008-04-03 |accessdate=2014-11-07 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121012034705/http://www.people.com/people/article/0%2C%2C20188076%2C00.html |archivedate=2012-10-12 |publisher=Time Inc. }}</ref>。克鲁斯的[[律师|律师]]声称，发布克鲁斯身穿戏服照片的媒体将遭到起诉<ref name="ninemsn">{{cite news | last = Naidu | first = Rajeshni | title = Tom Cruise fat suit photos banned | publisher = National Nine News | date = 2007-11-20 | url = http://news.ninemsn.com.au/article.aspx?id=326885 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120929211959/http://news.ninemsn.com.au/article.aspx?id=326885 | archivedate = 2012-09-29 | accessdate = 2012-09-29}}</ref>。他们联系了多个发布图片的网站，很快就已将这些照片删除<ref name="SpoilSurprise">{{cite web | last = Carroll | first = Larry | accessdate = 2014-11-07 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.mtv.com/news/1574707/tom-cruises-tropic-thunder-fat-suit-photo-leaks-online-spoils-his-secret-cameo/ | title = Tom Cruise 'Tropic Thunder' Photo Spoils Surprise | publisher = MTV Networks | date = 2007-11-20 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141107142335/http://www.mtv.com/news/1574707/tom-cruises-tropic-thunder-fat-suit-photo-leaks-online-spoils-his-secret-cameo/ | archivedate = 2014-11-07}}</ref>。克鲁斯的一位发言人表示：“克鲁斯先生的扮相本应给予他在全世界的粉丝以惊喜，[[狗仔队|狗仔队]]毁掉了我们留给影迷们去发掘的乐趣”<ref name="SpoilSurprise" />。这张照片首先是由摄影机构{{lang|en|INF}}发布的，该机构发表声明回应称：“这些照片是在没有违反任何[[刑法|刑事]]或[[私法|民事法律]]的情况下拍摄的，我们已经决定立即停止其发布”<ref name="FatSuitTom" /><ref name="ninemsn" />。

托比·马奎尔是在最后关头确定出镜的演员，他只能在片场停留两小时拍摄《撒旦小径》的镜头<ref name="DVDCommSatAll">{{cite video | title = Tropic Thunder-(Filmmaker Commentary by Ben Stiller, Justin Theroux, Stuart Cornfeld, Jeff Man, John Toll, and Greg Hayden) | medium = Blu-ray Disc | publisher = DreamWorks | time = 2:45 | date = 2008-11-18}}</ref>。唐尼表示，他对马奎尔同意客串出演这一角色感到意外，并且还觉得两人在本片中的演出就像是之前在[[2000年电影|2000年电影]]《[[奇迹小子|奇迹小子]]》中共同演出的“[[业|因果报应]]”，该片中两人的角色有过[[一夜情|一夜情]]<ref name="WonderBoysAlley" />。由于克鲁斯需要出演格罗斯曼，因此[[欧文·威尔森|欧文·威尔森]]获选出演里克·佩克。但威尔森因2007年8月试图[[自杀|自杀]]而退出了剧组，取代他的人选是[[马修·麦康纳|马修·麦康纳]]<ref name="OwenRecast">{{cite news | title = Owen Wilson comedy role is recast | publisher = BBC News | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/7004326.stm | date = 2007-09-20 | archivedate = 2013-12-14 | accessdate = 2014-11-07 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131214150734/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/7004326.stm}}</ref>。

=== 拍摄 ===
剧组曾考虑将[[南加州|南加州]]和[[墨西哥|墨西哥]]作为主要拍摄地点，但本片的大部分镜头最终都是在[[夏威夷群岛|夏威夷群岛]]的[[考艾岛|考艾岛]]取景，斯蒂勒的家就在这里<ref name="SoCal">{{cite news | last = Levy | first = Emanuel | title = Tropic Thunder: Making of a War Movie Satire | publisher = Emanuel Levy Cinema 24/7 | accessdate = 2014-11-07 | url = http://emanuellevy.com/comment/tropic-thunder-making-of-a-war-movie-satire-6/ | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120826013621/http://www.emanuellevy.com/comment/tropic-thunder-making-of-a-war-movie-satire-6/ | archivedate = 2012-08-26 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。剧组之所以选择考艾岛而非墨西哥，主要是因为他们通过与考艾岛电影协会谈判后达成协议，在夏威夷州以内的支出可以获得税收抵免<ref name="Kauai">{{cite news | last = Longwell | first = Todd | title = Hawaii is enticing major filming productions | work = The Hollywood Reporter | date = 2008-05-16}}</ref>。[[摄影师|摄影师]]约翰·托尔表示，考艾岛入选的另一个原因是当地的气候与[[越南|越南]]相似，并且同样有着密集的树林枝叶和各种各样的地形<ref name="JohnKodak">{{cite news | title = Behind The Scenes with John Toll on Tropic Thunder | publisher = Kodak | url = http://motion.kodak.com/motion/education/news_and_events/news/2008/Aug18_1.htm | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120722024349/http://motion.kodak.com/motion/education/news_and_events/news/2008/Aug18_1.htm | archivedate = 2012-07-22| accessdate = 2014-11-07}}</ref>。早在2004年时，斯蒂勒就对考艾岛做了斟查，看这里是否适合成为《热带惊雷》的取景地点。他在6个星期里花了超过25小时使用[[全地形车|全地形车]]、船只和直升机对岛上进行探索<ref name="SoCal" /><ref name="DVDCommScout">{{cite video | title = Tropic Thunder-(Designing the Thunder) | medium = Blu-ray Disc | publisher = DreamWorks | time = 1:45 | date = 2008-11-18}}</ref>。2006年，[[梦工厂|梦工厂]]批准电影开拍，其前制准备工作持续了6个月，其中大部分时间都花在对更多潜在取景地点的堪测上<ref name="TrailerEddie" /><ref name="SoCal" />。片中洛杉矶以及室内镜头的拍摄是在好莱坞的[[环球影业|环球影业]][[片场系统|片场]]进行<ref name="SoCal" />。
[[File:TropicThunderSetAbove07.jpg|thumb]]的片场。]]

《热带惊雷》是5年来在考艾岛摄制的第一部大型制片公司作品。拍摄工作完成后，影片的拍摄规模创下岛上的新纪录，为地方经济贡献了超过6000万美元<ref name="SoCal" /><ref name="CutsImpact">{{cite news |last=Levine |first=Michael |title=State film office cuts impact Kaua‘i |work=[http://www.kauaiworld.com/ ''The Garden Island''] |date=2009-10-07 |url=http://thegardenisland.com/news/local/article_d550376b-31ae-5779-a238-d947e4860c24.html |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5u4a8PPfH?url=http://thegardenisland.com/news/local/article_d550376b-31ae-5779-a238-d947e4860c24.html |archivedate=2010-11-07 |accessdate=2014-11-07 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。《夏威夷电影和录像杂志》（{{lang|en|''Hawaii Film & Video Magazine''}}）执行主编蒂姆·瑞安（{{lang|en|Tim Ryan}}）对此表示：“我认为，《热带惊雷》会给考艾岛带来电影制作领域长期中断而迫切需要的宣传……这应该可以让考艾岛重新进入电影拍摄的考量雷达范围”<ref name="GardenIsland">{{cite news|last=Vines |first=Todd A. |title=Feel the 'Tropic Thunder' |work=[http://www.kauaiworld.com/ ''The Garden Island''] |date=2007-05-03 |accessdate=2014-11-07 |url=http://thegardenisland.com/news/article_5e1e0b6f-eea0-5365-bf86-b35d4581ec8a.html |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110811072408/http://thegardenisland.com/news/article_5e1e0b6f-eea0-5365-bf86-b35d4581ec8a.html |archivedate=2011-08-11 }}</ref>。前期制作人员从2006年12月开始来到岛上工作，主体拍摄工作则在2007年7月展开，拍摄工作持续了13个多星期，在岛上至少7个地点取景<ref name="GardenIsland" /><ref name="StillerVogue">{{cite news | last = Green | first = Adam | title = Fool's Gold | work = Men's Vogue | date = 2008-08 | url = http://www.mensvogue.com/magazine/articles/2008/08/ben-stiller | accessdate = 2008-12-16 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20081216085902/http://www.mensvogue.com/magazine/articles/2008/08/ben-stiller | archivedate = 2008-12-16}}</ref>。大部分拍摄地点不是私人领地就是受到保护的栖息地<ref name="CutsImpact" />。剧组还找来岛上500位居民扮演片中的村民<ref name="GardenIsland" />。岛上有两组人员同时进行拍摄，空中还有直升机拍摄队<ref name="JohnTreks">{{cite news|last=Fisher |first=Bob |title=John Toll, ASC Treks Through the Hawaiian Jungle for Tropic Thunder |work=''ICG Magazine'' |date=2008-08 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130528132037/http://icgmagazine.com/2008/aug/aug08.html |accessdate=2014-11-07 |url=http://icgmagazine.com/2008/aug/aug08.html |archivedate=2013-05-28 }}</ref>。大部分外景以及片尾镜头拍摄所用的桥梁都是在三个月里搭建起来的<ref name="DVDCommSets3">{{cite video | title = Tropic Thunder-(Designing the Thunder) | medium = Blu-ray Disc | publisher = DreamWorks | time = 7:07 | date = 2008-11-18}}</ref>。岛上天气变化无常，产生的降水和照明问题对拍摄产生不利影响<ref name="DVDCommRain">{{cite video | title = Tropic Thunder-(Designing the Thunder) | medium = Blu-ray Disc | publisher = DreamWorks | time = 3:04 | date = 2008-11-18}}</ref><ref name="DVDCommLight">{{cite video | title = Tropic Thunder-(Filmmaker Commentary by Ben Stiller, Justin Theroux, Stuart Cornfeld, Jeff Man, John Toll, and Greg Hayden) | medium = Blu-ray Disc | publisher = DreamWorks | time = 6:55 | date = 2008-11-18}}</ref>。由于地形复杂，剧组在转移设备和演员时也面临困难<ref name="JohnKodak" />。

勇士公司获聘为电影提供咨询，确保片中战争场面和演员的装束看上去更真实。多位前美国军人教导几位演员如何手持武器、如何开火并重新装弹，还教他们各种战术动作<ref name="WarFilming">{{cite news | last = Levy | first = Emanuel | title = Tropic Thunder: Shooting the Battle Scenes | publisher = Emanuel Levy | url = http://emanuellevy.com/comment/tropic-thunder-shooting-the-battle-scenes-4/ | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120826013747/http://www.emanuellevy.com/comment/tropic-thunder-shooting-the-battle-scenes-4/ | archivedate = 2012-08-26 | accessdate = 2014-11-08}}</ref>。电影开头的战争场面动用了50名特技演员，并且拍摄时间超过3个星期<ref name="DVDComm3Weeks">{{cite video | title = Tropic Thunder-(Cast Commentary by Ben Stiller, Jack Black, and Robert Downey Jr.) | medium = Blu-ray Disc | publisher = DreamWorks | time = 10:20 | date = 2008-11-18}}</ref><ref name="DVDCommStuntMen">{{cite video | title = Tropic Thunder-(The Hot LZ) | medium = Blu-ray Disc | publisher = DreamWorks | time = 2:24 | date = 2008-11-18}}</ref>。为了映射出拍摄所需的摄像机角度，剧组还使用了[[分镜|样片]]制作手段<ref name="DVDCommStoryboard">{{cite video | title = Tropic Thunder-(The Hot LZ) | medium = Blu-ray Disc | publisher = DreamWorks | time = 4:44 | date = 2008-11-18}}</ref>。

=== 特效 ===
影片中约500个[[视觉效果|视觉效果]]镜头涉及的各种场景和元素由6家公司共同制作，并且在一段时间里每周都会根据试映时观众的反应做调整<ref name="VFXTT">{{cite news | last = Bennett | first = Tara | title = Tropic Thunder: Doing Funny VFX | publisher = [http://vfxworld.com/ VFX World] | date = 2008-08-15 | archivedate = 2014-11-08 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.awn.com/vfxworld/tropic-thunder-doing-funny-vfx | accessdate = 2014-11-08 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141108132234/http://www.awn.com/vfxworld/tropic-thunder-doing-funny-vfx}}</ref>。{{lang|en|CIS}}视觉特效集团协助制作了《大热天{{lang|en|VI}}：全球消融》的伪预告片，还有20段家用媒体中增加的镜头内容<ref name="VFXTDVD">{{cite news | title = Tropic Thunder's Visual Effects Play Up The Laughs | publisher = [http://vfxworld.com/ VFX World] | date = 2008-08-18 | accessdate = 2014-11-08 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.awn.com/news/tropic-thunders-visual-effects-play-laughs | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141108133410/http://www.awn.com/news/tropic-thunders-visual-effects-play-laughs | archivedate = 2014-11-08}}</ref>。为了增强电影的喜剧效果，片中一些爆炸、遭遇战之类大场面经过特别处理，看起来更具破坏力。视觉效果总监迈克尔·芬克（{{lang|en|Michael Fink}}）针对片中夸张的爆炸镜头表示：“我们竭力让直升机迫降坠毁的{{lang|en|[[计算机绘图|CG]]}}镜头看起来更真实。本（·斯蒂勒）对此态度坚决，但与此同时，他又希望爆炸场面看起来更壮观。当你看到直升机触地时，那（爆炸）看起来仿佛是装满了[[汽油|汽油]]一般！本出演的军士角色也是这么回事，他几乎是挡住了一颗[[手榴弹|手榴弹]]……我在[[美国陆军|陆军]]服役三年，从来没有哪颗手榴弹会像那样爆炸……但这在电影里是个非常有戏剧性的时刻，看起来实在很酷……而且感觉也很真实。”<ref name="VFXTT" />

电影片头大型[[凝固汽油弹|凝固汽油弹]]爆炸的镜头需要一个长达137米的炸药容器，其中盛有4165升汽油和[[柴油|柴油]]燃料。剧组在确定所需的摄像机角度和照明需要后，将爆炸中需要用到的所有棕榈树都移动到了特定地点<ref name="DVDCommTrees">{{cite video | title = Tropic Thunder-(Filmmaker Commentary by Ben Stiller, Justin Theroux, Stuart Cornfeld, Jeff Man, John Toll, and Greg Hayden) | medium = Blu-ray Disc | publisher = DreamWorks | time = 11:54 | date = 2008-11-18}}</ref>。由于这场仅持续1.25秒的爆炸规模和耗资都很庞大，因此镜头只拍了一次，并且动用了12台摄像机来记录<ref name="WarFilming" /><ref name="Napalm">{{cite news | last = Amodio | first = Joseph | title = Explosive laughter: In the combat spoof 'Tropic Thunder,' director Ben Stiller makes sure war is hell, especially on the actors | work = Newsday | format = Fee required | date = 2008-08-10 | accessdate = 2014-11-08 | url = http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/newsday/doc/280252598.html?FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&type=current&date=Aug%2010,%202008&author=JOSEPH%20V%20AMODIO&pub=Newsday&edition=&startpage=n/a&desc=Explosive%20laughter:%20In%20the%20combat%20spoof%20'Tropic%20Thunder,'%20director | archive-date = 2016-03-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160306211739/http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/newsday/doc/280252598.html?FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS%3AFT&type=current&date=Aug%2010%2C%202008&author=JOSEPH%20V%20AMODIO&pub=Newsday&edition=&startpage=n%2Fa&desc=Explosive%20laughter%3A%20In%20the%20combat%20spoof%20%27Tropic%20Thunder%2C%27%20director | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="DVDComm12C">{{cite video | title = Tropic Thunder-(Filmmaker Commentary by Ben Stiller, Justin Theroux, Stuart Cornfeld, Jeff Man, John Toll, and Greg Hayden) | medium = Blu-ray Disc | publisher = DreamWorks | time = 15:45 | date = 2008-11-18}}</ref>。为保障工作人员和演员的安全，所需的[[雷管|雷管]]直到爆炸前1小时才安装，并且任何人都不得接近雷管方圆120米内<ref name="DVDCommOneHour">{{cite video | title = Tropic Thunder-(Blowing Shit Up) | medium = Blu-ray Disc | publisher = DreamWorks | time = 2:39 | date = 2008-11-18}}</ref><ref name="DVDCommExplosion">{{cite video | title = Tropic Thunder-(Filmmaker Commentary by Ben Stiller, Justin Theroux, Stuart Cornfeld, Jeff Man, John Toll, and Greg Hayden) | medium = Blu-ray Disc | publisher = DreamWorks | time = 12:18 | date = 2008-11-18}}</ref>。整场爆炸由12次较小规模的爆炸组成，产生的[[蘑菇云|蘑菇云]]有110米高<ref name="WarFilming" /><ref name="Napalm" />。丹尼·麦克布耐德出演的科迪·安德伍德是唯一在爆炸镜头中真实出现的人物，其他角色则都是通过数字手段添加进去<ref name="DVDCommCody">{{cite video | title = Tropic Thunder-(Filmmaker Commentary by Ben Stiller, Justin Theroux, Stuart Cornfeld, Jeff Man, John Toll, and Greg Hayden) | medium = Blu-ray Disc | publisher = DreamWorks | time = 15:27 | date = 2008-11-18}}</ref>。片尾桥梁爆炸的镜头使用了9台摄像机一起记录，这也是片中最后几个用这么多台摄影机拍摄的镜头之一，为了保障安全，剧组人员需要撤离到爆炸地点910米外<ref name="DVDCommStuntMen2">{{cite video | title = Tropic Thunder-(The Hot LZ) | medium = Blu-ray Disc | publisher = DreamWorks | time = 5:18 | date = 2008-11-18}}</ref>。

== 宣传 ==
[[File:BenStillerTropicThunderPendleton.jpg|thumb]]
2008年4月，影片发行了首部预告片。《[[卡尔加里先驱报|卡尔加里先驱报]]》（{{lang|en|''Calgary Herald''}}）给予这段预告片的评分是3（最高为5），称：“这（部电影）要么会很不错，要么就会非常非常糟糕”<ref name="CalHerVB">{{cite news|url=http://www.canada.com/calgaryherald/news/story.html?id=8eb116a3-a5e5-4e05-8571-d9608d65e6cf |title=Trailer Treasures & Trash: A Sneak Peek at the hottest trailers |publisher=Canwest News Service |work=Calgary Herald |date=2008-04-25 |archivedate=2012-11-08 |accessdate=2014-11-08 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121108160559/http://www.canada.com/calgaryherald/news/story.html?id=8eb116a3-a5e5-4e05-8571-d9608d65e6cf }}</ref>。《[[娱乐周刊|娱乐周刊]]》的加里·苏斯曼（{{lang|en|Gary Susman}}）怀疑电影会“变成恰恰是它所嘲弄的那种臃肿的[[动作片|动作片]]怪兽”<ref name="EWBloated">{{cite news | accessdate = 2014-11-08 | url = http://popwatch.ew.com/2008/03/19/tropic-thunder-2/ | title = Trailer Blazer: 'Tropic Thunder' | work = Entertainment Weekly | date = 2008-03-19 | archivedate = 2013-06-03 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130603030327/http://popwatch.ew.com/2008/03/19/tropic-thunder-2/ }}</ref>。这段预告片获得了第9届[[金拖车奖|金拖车奖]]最佳喜剧电影预告片奖<ref name="GTA">{{cite news | last = Kroll | first = Justin | url = http://variety.com/2008/film/news/golden-trailer-awards-honor-previews-1117985444/ | title = Golden Trailer Awards honor previews | work = Variety | date = 2008-05-09 | accessdate = 2014-11-08 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141108145958/http://variety.com/2008/film/news/golden-trailer-awards-honor-previews-1117985444/ | archivedate = 2014-11-08}}</ref>。[[梦工厂|梦工厂]]还发行了一段[[预告片|红带预告片]]（即[[美国电影分级制度#美國電影協會電影分級|R級]]預告片），是该公司首次用这种预告片来宣传其电影<ref name="Redband">{{cite news | last = Cieply | first = Michael | accessdate = 2014-11-08 | url = http://www.nytimes.com/2008/08/02/movies/02trop.html | title = New Film Tests Crudity's Limits | work = The New York Times | date = 2008-08-02 | publisher = The New York Times Company | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090310093710/http://www.nytimes.com/2008/08/02/movies/02trop.html | archivedate = 2009-03-10}}</ref>。

斯蒂勒、唐尼和布莱克一起出现在《[[美国偶像|美国偶像]]》第7季的最后一集节目中，使用[[葛蕾蒂絲·奈特|葛蕾蒂絲·奈特]]（Gladys Knight）的演出视频片段模仿她和[[葛蕾蒂絲·奈特與種子合唱團|種子合唱團]]的演出<ref name="EWInterview">{{cite news|last=Rottenberg |first=Josh |title='Tropic Thunder': Boys Gone Wild! |work=Entertainment Weekly |date=2008-08-15 |deadurl=no |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20217667,00.html |archivedate=2014-09-22 |accessdate=2014-11-08 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140922013627/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0%2C%2C20217667%2C00.html }}</ref>。三位男演员之后还在[[2008年MTV电影大奖|2008年MTV电影大奖]]颁奖晚会上表演了节目，主要内容是他们打算制作一段成功的[[病毒视讯|病毒视讯]]来为电影宣传，但却导致了尴尬的结果<ref name="EWInterview" />。2008年9月，斯蒂勒和唐尼出席[[圣塞瓦斯蒂安国际电影节|圣塞瓦斯蒂安国际电影节]]为影片宣传。影片在电影节上放映，但没有进入竞赛单元<ref name="SanSebast">{{cite news | last = Masters | first = Charles | title = 'Thunder' stars give San Sebastian a jolt | work = The Hollywood Reporter | date = 2008-09-21 | accessdate = 2014-11-08 | url = http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/thunder-stars-give-san-sebastian-119554 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141108152740/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/thunder-stars-give-san-sebastian-119554 | archivedate = 2014-11-08}}</ref>。

2008年4月到2008年8月电影正式发行的这段时间里，《热带惊雷》一共进行了超过250场次促销式放映<ref name="NYTBoycott">{{cite news | last = Cieply | first = Michael | title = Nationwide 'Thunder' Boycott in the Works | work = The New York Times | date = 2008-08-10 | url = http://www.nytimes.com/2008/08/11/movies/11thun.html | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140325060246/http://www.nytimes.com/2008/08/11/movies/11thun.html | archivedate = 2014-03-25 | publisher = The New York Times Company | accessdate = 2014-11-08}}</ref>。2008年8月3日，斯蒂勒、唐尼和布莱克到访[[彭德尔顿营海军陆战队基地|彭德尔顿营]]，这里是[[美国海军陆战队|美国海军陆战队]]位于[[加利福尼亚州|加利福尼亚州]]的一处基地，几位演员在此向上千名军人及他们的家人放映了本片。这次放映是以[[美国联合服务组织|美国联合服务组织]]的名义进行，并且演员们是乘坐直升机和[[悍马_(军用汽车)|悍马车]]前往放映点<ref name="CampScreening">{{cite news | last = Breznican | first = Anthony | accessdate = 2014-11-08 | deadurl = no | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/movies/news/2008-08-04-tropic-thunder-inside_N.htm | title = 'Tropic Thunder' stars take Marine base by storm | work = USA Today | date = 2008-08-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121102091754/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/movies/news/2008-08-04-tropic-thunder-inside_N.htm | archivedate = 2012-11-02}}</ref>。2008年8月8日，一部长约30分钟的虚构《{{lang|en|E!}}好莱坞真实故事》特别节目面世，其内容为《热带惊雷》的制作过程；[[电子游戏|电子游戏]]《[[虹彩六號：拉斯維加斯2|虹彩六號：拉斯維加斯2]]》中加入了以本片为主题的寻宝活动，斯蒂勒还同意根据本片创作的{{lang|en|[[Facebook|Facebook]]}}在线游戏应用中使用自己的肖像<ref name="RainbowSix">{{cite news | last = Radd | first = David | url = http://www.businessweek.com/stories/2008-08-13/tropic-thunders-perfect-storm-of-cross-promotionbusinessweek-business-news-stock-market-and-financial-advice | title = Tropic Thunder's Perfect Storm of Cross-Promotion | work = BusinessWeek | date = 2008-08-13 | archivedate = 2014-11-08 | accessdate = 2014-11-08 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141108155243/http://www.businessweek.com/stories/2008-08-13/tropic-thunders-perfect-storm-of-cross-promotionbusinessweek-business-news-stock-market-and-financial-advice}}</ref><ref name="FacebookGame">{{cite news | last = Richards | first = Jonathan | accessdate = 2011-06-11 | deadurl = yes | url = http://business.timesonline.co.uk/tol/business/industry_sectors/technology/article4454170.ece | title = Computer games move into guerrilla marketing | work = The Times | date = 2008-08-04 | archivedate = 2011-06-11 | location = London | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110611205220/http://business.timesonline.co.uk/tol/business/industry_sectors/technology/article4454170.ece}}</ref>。

派拉蒙电影公司宣布，为了配合影片上映，该公司将推出其中的机能性饮料“屁股汗液”<ref name="BootySweat">{{cite news |last=Brodesser-Akner |first=Claude |title=Paramount Breaks Out the Booty Sweat |work=Advertising Age |date=2008-06-26 |url=http://adage.com/article/madisonvine-news/paramount-breaks-booty-sweat/128031/ |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5u4bANa8r?url=http://adage.com/madisonandvine/article?article_id=128031 |archivedate=2010-11-07 |accessdate=2014-11-08 }}</ref>。派拉蒙消费品总裁迈克尔·科科伦（{{lang|en|Michael Corcoran}}）对此表示：“我们非常兴奋，因为它（指饮料）有着远远超出电影（发行）生命周期的潜力”<ref name="BootySweat" />。该饮料通过多家大学书店、[[亚马逊公司|亚马逊网站]]及其他零售商销售<ref name="BootySweat" />。

=== 虚假网站和伪纪录片 ===
电影中的几位主要角色都是演员，制片公司为此制作了这些“演员”及其之前演出电影的虚假网站。8月4日，由于有残疾人权利倡导人士提出抗议，梦工厂撤掉了片中虚构电影《笨蛋阿瓜》的网站。<ref name="SimpleJackPulled">{{cite news | last = Siegel | first = Tatiana | title = DreamWorks logs off 'Simple' site | work = Variety | date = 2008-08-05 | deadurl = no | url = http://variety.com/2008/digital/news/dreamworks-logs-off-simple-site-1117990121/ | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141109052429/http://variety.com/2008/digital/news/dreamworks-logs-off-simple-site-1117990121/ | archivedate = 2014-11-09 | accessdate = 2014-11-09}}</ref>

2008年7月中旬，[[伪纪录片|伪纪录片]]《疯狂的雨》（{{lang|en|''Rain of Madness''}}）的伪预告片面世，是恶搞《[[黑暗之心：現代啟示錄拍攝紀錄|黑暗之心：現代啟示錄拍攝紀錄]]》（{{lang|en|''Hearts of Darkness: A Filmmaker's Apocalypse''}}）的作品<ref name="MadnessEW">{{cite news | last = Susman | first = Gary | title = Trailer Blazer: 'Tropic Thunder' mockumentary 'Rain of Madness' | work = Entertainment Weekly | date = 2008-07-09 | url = http://popwatch.ew.com/2008/07/09/rain-madness-tr/ | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140519165232/http://popwatch.ew.com/2008/07/09/rain-madness-tr/ | archivedate = 2014-05-19 | accessdate = 2014-11-09 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。编剧贾斯汀·塞洛克斯成为其中虚构的纪录片电影人扬·于尔根（{{lang|en|Jan Jürgen}}），记录下《热带惊雷》戏中戏的“幕后故事”。《热带惊雷》正式发行前，这部伪纪录片还推出了海报和官方网站。电影上映后，伪纪录片通过{{lang|en|[[iTunes_Store|iTunes Store]]}}发布，并且也包含在家用媒体中<ref name="RoMTT">{{cite news | last = Gil | first = Billy | title = DreamWorks Offers 'Tropic Thunder' Featurette on iTunes | work = Home Media Magazine | date = 2008-08-27 | accessdate = 2014-11-09 | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.homemediamagazine.com/dreamworks-offers-tropic-thunder-featurette-itunes-13409 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120722080729/http://www.homemediamagazine.com/dreamworks-offers-tropic-thunder-featurette-itunes-13409 | archivedate = 2012年7月22日 }}</ref>。派拉蒙公司广告经理艾米·鲍威尔（{{lang|en|Amy Powell}}）针对《疯狂的雨》的发行时机表示：“我们总是觉得，人们会在水冷器旁谈论《热带惊雷》，这正是我们要在电影上映两周后发布《疯狂的雨》的原因：让这种有利的氛围持续下去”<ref name="RainMadnessQuote">{{cite news | last = Siegel | first = Tatiana | title = 'Madness' steals 'Tropic's' thunder | work = Variety | accessdate = 2014-11-09 | deadurl = no | url = http://variety.com/2008/music/news/madness-steals-tropic-s-thunder-1117991366/ | date = 2008-08-29 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141103210116/http://variety.com/2008/music/news/madness-steals-tropic-s-thunder-1117991366/ | archivedate = 2014-11-03}}</ref>。

== 发行 ==
=== 院线上映 ===
2008年8月11日，《热带惊雷》在加利福尼亚州[[西木区|西木区]]的曼村剧院[[首演|首映]]，两天后再进入大范围上映。多个残障人士团体的成员前来抗议片中对[[智能障碍|智障]]人士的刻画<ref name="USATProtest">{{cite news | last = Puig | first = Claudia | title = Protesters find no humor in 'Tropic Thunder' | work = USA Today | date = 2008-08-12 | deadurl = no | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/movies/news/2008-08-12-tropic-protests_N.htm | accessdate = 2014-11-09 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121023234754/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/movies/news/2008-08-12-tropic-protests_N.htm | archivedate = 2012-10-23}}</ref>。这些组织透露，这是他们首次聚集到一起针对一场活动提出抗议<ref name="USATProtest" />。这导致首映式上通常畅通无阻的红地毯被3米高的栅栏阻挡，并且在场的保安人员数量也有增加<ref name="ProtestPremiere">{{cite news | last = Siegel | first = Tatiana | title = 'Tropic' premiere brings protest | work = Variety | date = 2008-08-11 | url = http://variety.com/2008/film/news/tropic-premiere-brings-protest-1117990426/ | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141109093352/http://variety.com/2008/film/news/tropic-premiere-brings-protest-1117990426/ | archivedate = 2014-11-09 | accessdate = 2014-11-09 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。9月影片在英国首映时没有出现人群抗议的情况<ref name="ProtestPremiereUK">{{cite news | last = Rohrer | first = Finlo | title = The path from cinema to playground | publisher = BBC News | date = 2008-09-22 | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/magazine/7629376.stm | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130930171415/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/magazine/7629376.stm | archivedate = 2013-09-30 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2013-09-30}}</ref>。

影片原计划于2008年7月11日在北美上映，但一度推迟到8月15日，最终又一次调整到8月13日<ref name="ReleaseDateShuffle">{{cite news | last = McClintoc | first = Pamela | title = Studios shuffle 2009 summer sked | work = Variety | date = 2008-08-07 | url = http://variety.com/2008/film/news/studios-shuffle-2009-summer-sked-1117990240/ | archivedate = 2014-11-09 | accessdate = 2014-11-09 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141109094236/http://variety.com/2008/film/news/studios-shuffle-2009-summer-sked-1117990240/}}</ref>。为此[[二十世纪福克斯|二十世纪福克斯]]将家庭喜剧《[[戴夫号飞船|戴夫号飞船]]》提前到7月空档期<ref name="ReleaseDateShuffle" />。8月13日还是家庭动画长片《[[星球大战动画：复制人战争_(电影)|星球大战：克隆战争]]》和[[恐怖片|恐怖片]]《[[鬼镜|鬼镜]]》（{{lang|en|''Mirrors''}}）上映的第一个周末。制片公司认为，8月的第三个星期由于许多学生都已返校，因此上映电影的票房成绩会不及暑假早期发行的作品<ref name="AugustWeekend">{{cite news | last = Friedman | first = Josh | title = It's a matter of timing; Studios are clinging to weekends that have worked for them before | work = Los Angeles Times | date = 2008-05-22 | format = Fee required | accessdate = 2014-11-09 | url = http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/latimes/doc/422353046.html?FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&type=current&date=May%2022,%202008&author=Josh%20Friedman&pub=Los%20Angeles%20Times&edition=&startpage=&desc=MOVIE%20PROJECTOR;%20It's%20a%20matter%20of%20timing;%20Studios%20are%20cli | archive-date = 2016-03-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160306211008/http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/latimes/doc/422353046.html?FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS%3AFT&type=current&date=May%2022%2C%202008&author=Josh%20Friedman&pub=Los%20Angeles%20Times&edition=&startpage=&desc=MOVIE%20PROJECTOR%3B%20It%27s%20a%20matter%20of%20timing%3B%20Studios%20are%20cli | dead-url = no }}</ref>。之前曾有多部[[美国电影分级制度|R级]]喜剧片——如《[[四十岁的老处男|四十岁的老处男]]》和《[[太坏了|太坏了]]》（{{lang|en|''Superbad''}}）——也是在8月中旬上映，并且都收获了良好的票房成绩。针对《热带惊雷》的上映日期，派拉蒙公司副总裁罗布·摩尔（{{lang|en|Rob Moore}}）表示：“对于暑假即将结束的年轻人来说，你就想开心一场，忘掉自己还要上学。有什么能比一部疯狂的喜剧更合适呢？”<ref name="AugustWeekend" />

=== 票房成绩 ===
梦工厂执行总裁斯泰西·斯奈德（{{lang|en|Stacey Snider}}）认为，影片上映的第一个周末会进账3000万美元左右，并且会像《[[波拉特_(电影)|波拉特]]》一样取得美加两国1.29亿美元，全球票房2.6亿美元的较大成功<ref name="Redband" />。《热带惊雷》上映前，《[[蝙蝠侠：黑暗骑士|蝙蝠侠：黑暗骑士]]》已经占据票房[[冠军|冠军]]位置4个星期。加拿大《[[全国邮报|全国邮报]]》的鲍勃·汤普森（{{lang|en|Bob Thompson}}）估计，《热带惊雷》上映第一个周末的票房将超越《蝙蝠侠：黑暗骑士》<ref name="NationalKnight">{{cite news |last=Thompson |first=Bob |accessdate=2010-11-07 |url=http://network.nationalpost.com/np/blogs/theampersand/archive/2008/08/11/bob-thompson-tropic-thunder-should-out-do-the-dark-knight.aspx |title=Bob Thompson: Tropic Thunder should out do The Dark Knight |work=National Post |date=2008-08-11 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5u4cYTyLL?url=http://network.nationalpost.com/np/blogs/theampersand/archive/2008/08/11/bob-thompson-tropic-thunder-should-out-do-the-dark-knight.aspx |archivedate=2010-11-07 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。《[[娱乐周刊|娱乐周刊]]》在对暑期电影所做预测中估计，本片会以1亿4260万美元的成绩在美国暑期票房榜上排名第10<ref name="EWBoxOffice">{{cite news|title=Box Office Predictions |work=Entertainment Weekly |date=2008-04-25 |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20192529,00.html |accessdate=2014-11-09 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130603023958/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0%2C%2C20192529%2C00.html |archivedate=2013-06-03 }}</ref>。

《热带惊雷》在美国和加拿大的3319家电影院开映，前5天收入3684万5588美元。影片以2581万2796万美元的成绩超越同一周开始发行的《星球大战：克隆战争》和《鬼镜》，登上票房榜冠军宝座<ref name="BOXMOJO">{{cite web|url=http://boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=tropicthunder.htm |title=Tropic Thunder |work=Box Office Mojo |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141106100458/http://boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=tropicthunder.htm |deadurl=yes |accessdate=2014-11-09 |publisher=IMDb.com |archivedate=2014-11-06 }}</ref>。梦工厂发言人奇普·沙利文（{{lang|en|Chip Sullivan}}）对此表示：“老实说，我们惊呆了。它完全达到了我们的期望”<ref name="MSNBCBoxOffice">{{cite news | agency = Associated Press | title = 'Tropic Thunder' rumbles past 'Dark Knight' | publisher = NBCNEWS.com | date = 2008-08-17 | url = http://www.today.com/id/26254363 | accessdate = 2014-11-09 | deadurl = no | work = TODAY.com | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141109102831/http://www.today.com/id/26254363 | archivedate = 2014-11-09}}</ref>。国际市场方面，影片率先在俄罗斯的418家电影院和[[阿拉伯联合酋长国|阿拉伯联合酋长国]]的19所院线上映，分别进账220万和31.9万美元<ref name="VarietyForeignBOX">{{cite news | last = McNary | first = Dave | title = 'Mummy,' 'Knight' stay hot overseas | work = Variety | date = 2008-08-17 | url = http://variety.com/2008/film/news/mummy-knight-stay-hot-overseas-1117990698/ | accessdate = 2014-11-09 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-11-09 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141109103146/http://variety.com/2008/film/news/mummy-knight-stay-hot-overseas-1117990698/}}</ref>。

《热带惊雷》在票房榜冠军位置共保持了3个星期，成为2008年继《蝙蝠侠：黑暗骑士》之后第二部达到这一目标的电影<ref name="EWThreeWeek">{{cite news|last=Rich |first=Joshua |title='Tropic Thunder': It's a Threepeat |deadurl=no |work=Entertainment Weekly |date=2008-09-01 |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20222770,00.html |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140922011225/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0%2C%2C20222770%2C00.html |archivedate=2014-09-22 |accessdate=2014-11-09 }}</ref><ref name="LATThreeWeek">{{cite news | last = Pandey | first = Swati | title = 'Tropic Thunder' holds top spot at box office | work = Los Angeles Times | date = 2008-08-25 | accessdate = 2014-11-09 | url = http://articles.latimes.com/2008/aug/25/business/fi-boxoffice25 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121024032732/http://articles.latimes.com/2008/aug/25/business/fi-boxoffice25 | archivedate = 2012-10-24}}</ref>。影片最多时在美国的3473家电影院上映，这个数字可以在2008年发行的电影中排到第25位<ref name="BOXMOJO" />。本片票房可以在2008年所有的{{lang|en|R}}级电影中排到第5名<ref name="BOXR">{{cite web | url = http://boxofficemojo.com/yearly/chart/mpaarating.htm?rating=R&yr=2008&p=.htm | title = 2008 Yearly Box Office By MPAA Rating | publisher = IMDb.com | work = [[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]] | accessdate = 2014-11-09 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141025094635/http://boxofficemojo.com/yearly/chart/mpaarating.htm?rating=R&yr=2008&p=.htm | archivedate = 2014-10-25}}</ref>，还以超过1.1亿美元的成绩刷新斯蒂勒导演电影的纪录<ref name="BOXMOJOStiller">{{cite web | url = http://boxofficemojo.com/people/chart/?view=Director&id=benstiller.htm | title = Ben Stiller — Director | publisher = IMDB.com | work = Box Office Mojo | accessdate = 2014-11-09 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141009213143/http://boxofficemojo.com/people/chart/?view=Director&id=benstiller.htm | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-11-09}}</ref>。最终本片一共在美加两国收入1亿1051万5313美元，全球市场共计1亿8807万2649美元<ref name="BOXMOJO" />。

=== 专业评价 ===
影片获得了评论员的普遍好评。根据[[烂番茄|烂番茄]]上收集的230篇评论文章，其中有190篇给出“新鲜”的正面评价，“新鲜度”为83%，平均得分7.1（最高10分）<ref name="RTfresh">{{cite web | accessdate = 2014-11-09 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140909053018/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/tropic_thunder/ | url = http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/tropic_thunder/ | title = Tropic Thunder | publisher = Rotten Tomatoes | archivedate = 2014-09-09}}</ref>。而{{lang|en|[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]}}上收集的39篇评论中则有30篇好评，无差评，9篇褒贬不一，[[加权平均数|综合评分]]71（最高100）<ref name="MetaCritic">{{cite web | url = http://www.metacritic.com/movie/tropic-thunder | title = Tropic Thunder | publisher = CBS Interactive Inc. | work = Metacritic | accessdate = 2014-11-09 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130115012559/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/tropic-thunder | archivedate = 2013-01-15}}</ref>。

2008年4月，《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》的迈克尔·奇普利（{{lang|en|Michael Cieply}}）在出席业内预映活动后认为，本片“……塑造成了（梦工厂）最优秀的新作”<ref name="cieply" />。《[[今日美国|今日美国]]》的克劳迪亚·普伊格（{{lang|en|Claudia Puig}}）给予电影正面评价，称“里面有一些疯狂的搞笑场面，虽然有一些部分很沉重，另一些则没有什么意义，幽默和讽刺的效果也被过于可怕的镜头削弱。但是，当进入搞笑段落时，那就真是很好笑”<ref name="USATReview">{{cite news | last = Puig | first = Claudia | title = 'Tropic Thunder' rolls with laughter | work = USA Today | date = 2008-08-12 | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/movies/reviews/2008-08-12-tropic-thunder_N.htm | accessdate = 2014-11-09 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121201060057/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/movies/reviews/2008-08-12-tropic-thunder_N.htm | archivedate = 2012-12-01 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。托德·麦卡锡（{{lang|en|Todd McCarthy}}）在《[[综艺_(杂志)|综艺]]》撰文批评了本片：“除了小罗伯特·唐尼和汤姆·克鲁斯轮番上阵带来的那些令人吃惊的漫画式可笑演出外，这些滑稽的动作其实相当薄弱、冗余而单调<ref name="VarietyReview">{{cite news | last = McCarthy | first = Todd | title = New U.S. Release — Tropic Thunder | work = Variety | date = 2008-07-25 | accessdate = 2014-11-09 | deadurl = no | url = http://variety.com/2008/film/reviews/tropic-thunder-1200508097/ | archivedate = 2014-11-09 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141109134037/http://variety.com/2008/film/reviews/tropic-thunder-1200508097/}}</ref>。《[[环球邮报|环球邮报]]》的里克·葛瑞恩（{{lang|en|Rick Groen}}）对电影的观感也不理想，称这是“……以喜剧为幌子的袭击——观看这部电影就像是被小丑打劫”<ref name="GlobeReview">{{cite news | last = Groen | first = Rick | title = Tropic Thunder fights for laughs, but dies trying | work = The Globe and Mail | date = 2008-08-13 | format = Registration required | location = Toronto}}</ref>。{{lang|en|J·R}}·琼斯（{{lang|en|J.R. Jones}}）在《[[芝加哥读者|芝加哥读者]]》上表示，“电影剩下的部分一直没能达到开场时那种欢闹的高度，这部分是因为大规模的电影制作扼杀了噱头，但主要也是因为这些噱头也太容易遭到扼杀了”<ref name="ChicagoReaderReview">{{cite news|last=Jones |first=J.R. |title=Tropic Thunder |work=Chicago Reader |date=2008-08-29 |url=http://www.chicagoreader.com/chicago/tropic-thunder/Film?oid=1071967 |archivedate=2013-05-22 |accessdate=2014-11-09 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130522024101/http://www.chicagoreader.com/chicago/tropic-thunder/Film?oid=1071967 }}</ref>。

电影开场前播映的伪预告片所获评价褒贬不一。《[[新闻周刊|新闻周刊]]》的大卫·安森（{{lang|en|David Ansen}}）给予这些预告片正面评价，称“《热带惊雷》是这个夏天最好笑的电影——事实上它是如此搞笑，电影都还没开始你就笑起来了”<ref name="BudgetNewsweek">{{cite news | last = Ansen | first = David | title = Days of 'Thunder' | work = Newsweek | date = 2008-08-02 | url = http://www.newsweek.com/movies-ben-stiller-list-director-87709 | accessdate = 2014-11-09 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140112222430/http://www.newsweek.com/movies-ben-stiller-list-director-87709 | archivedate = 2014-01-12 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。[[美联社|美联社]]的克里斯蒂·勒迈尔（{{lang|en|Christy Lemire}}）称这些预告片是“……这趟旅程里最棒的一部分”<ref name="LemireTrip">{{cite news | last = Lemire | first = Christy | title = 'Thunder' seamlessly blends comedy and action | publisher = CBS News | date = 2008-08-13 | accessdate = 2014-11-09 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.cbsnews.com/news/thunder-seamlessly-blends-comedy-action/ | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141109140753/http://www.cbsnews.com/news/thunder-seamlessly-blends-comedy-action/ | archivedate = 2014-11-09}}</ref>。不过《[[乡村之声|乡村之声]]》（{{lang|en|''The Village Voice''}}）的罗伯特·威隆斯基（{{lang|en|Robert Wilonsky}}）持负面看法，在他看来，这些预告片的喜剧形式过于浅显，缺乏深度<ref name="WioVillage">{{cite news|last=Wilonsky |first=Robert |title=''Tropic Thunder'': A Consummate Movie-Biz Parody |work=The Village Voice |date=2008-08-12 |archivedate=2014-01-02 |accessdate=2014-11-09 |deadurl=yes |url=http://www.villagevoice.com/2008-08-12/film/tropic-thunder-a-consummate-movie-biz-parody/ |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140102144413/http://www.villagevoice.com/2008-08-12/film/tropic-thunder-a-consummate-movie-biz-parody/ }}</ref>。

片中演员的表演所获评价同样褒贬不一。许多影评人称赞了唐尼的演员，称他非常“抢戏”、“……搞笑到出人意表……”会给观众带来他“节目中最美好的回忆”<ref name="WeitzJr">{{cite news | last = Weitzman | first = Elizabeth | title = Robert Downey Jr. is a must-see in ''Tropic Thunder'' | work = Daily News | date = 2008-08-12 | url = http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/movies/2008/08/12/2008-08-12_robert_downey_jr_is_a_mustsee_in_tropic_.html | archivedate = 2009-07-07 | accessdate = 2009-07-07 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090707144801/http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/movies/2008/08/12/2008-08-12_robert_downey_jr_is_a_mustsee_in_tropic_.html}}</ref><ref name="PeteRoll">{{cite news | last = Travers | first = Peter | title = Tropic Thunder | work = Rolling Stone | date = 2008-08-21 | accessdate = 2009-05-05 | url = http://www.rollingstone.com/reviews/movie/18270126/review/22187117/tropic_thunder | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090505225203/http://www.rollingstone.com/reviews/movie/18270126/review/22187117/tropic_thunder | archivedate = 2009-05-05 | deadurl = yes}}</ref><ref name="EbertJr">{{cite news | last = Ebert | first = Roger | authorlink = 罗杰·艾伯特 | title = Tropic Thunder | work = Chicago Sun-Times | date = 2008-08-12 | url = http://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/tropic-thunder-2008 | accessdate = 2014-11-09 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140831182150/http://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/tropic-thunder-2008 | archivedate = 2014-08-31}}</ref>。斯科特·范伯格在《[[洛杉矶时报|洛杉矶时报]]》上批评片中让唐尼诠释[[非裔美国人|非裔美国人]]的做法，他在评论中写道：“我无法想像在任何情况下（我）可以接受扮演黑人的演出，这和我无法想像自己接受（电影中出现）{{lang|en|N}}开头的那个词（指“{{lang|en|negro}}”，意为“黑鬼”，是对非裔美国人的蔑称）一样”<ref name="ScottFace">{{cite news | last = Feinberg | first = Scott | title = Celebrating Robert Downey Jr.'s blackface at the Oscars? (The week we inaugurate Obama?) | work = Los Angeles Times | date = 2009-01-16 | archivedate = 2010-12-06 | accessdate = 2010-12-06 | url = http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/files/2009/01/blackface-at-th.html | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20101206025350/http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/files/2009/01/blackface-at-th.html}}</ref>。萨拉·维尔科默森（{{lang|en|Sara Vilkomerson}}）表示，克鲁斯的配角演出“……有趣到让人惊喜”<ref name="SaraObser">{{cite news | last = Vilkomerson | first = Sara | title = Cruise Whips Out His Funny Bone | work = The New York Observer | date = 2008-08-05 | url = http://observer.com/2008/08/cruise-whips-out-his-funny-bone/ | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121011050428/http://observer.com/2008/08/cruise-whips-out-his-funny-bone/ | archivedate = 2012-10-11 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2014-11-09}}</ref>。《[[纽约_(杂志)|纽约]]》的洛根·希尔（{{lang|en|Logan Hill}}）则对克鲁斯的客串演出持负面看法，称这“……让他看起来有些失落，甚至可怜——仿佛他竭尽全力地想要引起那些逐渐背弃他的年轻影迷注意”<ref name="LogHillNY">{{cite news | last = Hill | first = Logan | title = Tom Cruise's ''Tropic Thunder'' Cameo Is Not Actually All That Funny | work = New York | date = 2008-08-08 | accessdate = 2014-11-09 | url = http://www.vulture.com/2008/08/tom_cruises_tropic_thunder_cam.html | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130118035323/http://www.vulture.com/2008/08/tom_cruises_tropic_thunder_cam.html | archivedate = 2013-01-18}}</ref>。

多位影评人针对片中一些谈论智障的台词进行了探讨。杜安·杜德克在《[[密尔沃基哨兵日报|密尔沃基哨兵日报]]》（{{lang|en|''Milwaukee Journal Sentinel''}}）称，电影“……刚好到了会（让人感到）冒犯的程度。由于影片还很好笑，其中毫无同情或怜悯，因此我们会奇怪自己怎么还能笑得出来”<ref name="DDWhy">{{cite news|last=Dudek |first=Duane |title=''Tropic Thunder'' funny but offensive |work=Milwaukee Journal Sentinel |date=2008-08-13 |url=http://www.jsonline.com/entertainment/movies/33039789.html |accessdate=2014-11-09 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140908114808/http://www.jsonline.com/entertainment/movies/33039789.html |archivedate=2014-09-08 }}</ref>。《[[华盛顿时报|华盛顿时报]]》的克里斯蒂安·托托（{{lang|en|Christian Toto}}）看法相反：“因其中多次用到‘白痴’一词……《热带惊雷》会引来特殊利益集团的炮火……但观众的眼睛是雪亮的，他们会知道这种幽默到底是指向何方，而且他们都笑得如此欢畅，以致于根本不会把这当成冒犯”<ref name="TotoFire">{{cite news | last = Horn | first = John | title = Film critics stand firm against 'Tropic Thunder' protests by advocates for the disabled | work = Los Angeles Times | date = 2008-08-15 | url = http://articles.latimes.com/2008/aug/15/entertainment/et-protests15 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140502232157/http://articles.latimes.com/2008/aug/15/entertainment/et-protests15 | archivedate = 2014-05-02 | accessdate = 2014-11-09 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。[[音乐电视网|音乐电视网]]的[[库尔特·洛德|库尔特·洛德]]（{{lang|en|Kurt Loder}}）也不觉得唐尼诠释非裔美国人有什么不妥：“如果说阿尔帕·西诺嘲弄拉扎勒斯朗诵黑人颂歌之举还不过是像歌词中的主题那样有些好笑的话，那么拉扎勒斯向史毕德曼解释他出演的《笨蛋阿瓜》以失败告终的原因——他不应该完全就是个白痴，而是应该用《[[阿甘正传|阿甘正传]]》中那种可爱的方式将人物软化，这样的解释实在是一针见血，让你屏息凝神、叹为观止”<ref name="KurtLoderMTV">{{cite news | last = Loder | first = Kurt | title = ''Tropic Thunder'': Say What? | publisher = MTV | date = 2008-08-13 | accessdate = 2014-11-09 | url = http://www.mtv.com/news/1592689/tropic-thunder-say-what-by-kurt-loder/ | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141109151839/http://www.mtv.com/news/1592689/tropic-thunder-say-what-by-kurt-loder/ | archivedate = 2014-11-09}}</ref>。

=== 评论名单 ===
2009年1月，《娱乐周刊》将《热带惊雷》评为“过去25年来25部最优秀的喜剧片”之一<ref name="25Great">{{cite news|title=25 Great Comedies From the Past 25 Years |work=Entertainment Weekly |date=2009-01-09 |deadurl=no |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20250815,00.html |archivedate=2013-06-03 |accessdate=2014-11-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130603023814/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0%2C%2C20250815%2C00.html }}</ref>。影片还登上了多位影评人的2008年十大佳片榜单<ref name="mctop08">{{cite web | deadurl = yes | url = http://search.metacritic.com/film/awards/2008/toptens.shtml | title = Metacritic: 2008 Film Critic Top Ten Lists | publisher = CBS Interactive Inc. | work = Metacritic | accessdate = 2012-03-14 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120314191601/http://search.metacritic.com/film/awards/2008/toptens.shtml | archivedate = 2012-03-14}}</ref>。[[斯蒂芬·金|斯蒂芬·金]]把本片排在第4位，称这是“今年最有趣，最有胆量的喜剧片”<ref name="King4">{{cite news|last=King |first=Stephen |title=Stephen King: 10 Best Movies of 2008 |work=Entertainment Weekly |date=2008-12-12 |archivedate=2013-06-03 |accessdate=2014-11-09 |deadurl=no |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/gallery/0,,20245818,00.html?iid=top25-Stephen+King%3A+10+best+movies+of+%2708 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130603021035/http://www.ew.com/ew/gallery/0%2C%2C20245818%2C00.html?iid=top25-Stephen%20King%3A%2010%20best%20movies%20of%20%2708 }}</ref>。《[[俄勒冈人|俄勒冈人]]》（{{lang|en|''The Oregonian''}}）的马克·莫汉（{{lang|en|Marc Mohan}}）将电影排名第6，同样属该报的迈克·拉塞尔（{{lang|en|Mike Russell}}）则将之排第7，与《[[纽约每日新闻|纽约每日新闻]]》的伊丽莎白·韦茨曼（{{lang|en|Elizabeth Weitzman}}）、《[[首映_(杂志)|首映]]》杂志、以及《[[旧金山纪事报|旧金山纪事报]]》的彼得·哈特劳布（{{lang|en|Peter Hartlaub}}）所排名次相同<ref name="mctop08" />。《新闻周刊》的大卫·安森将其排在第8位，《娱乐周刊》的丽莎·施瓦茨鲍姆（{{lang|en|Lisa Schwarzbaum}}）则排第10<ref name="mctop08" />。

=== 荣誉 ===
{{quote box|width=30em|quote=“对于我来说，这个角色专门谋求奥斯卡奖这点实在太好笑了。他（演戏）完全就是为了拿奥斯卡奖……讽刺的是，（现实生活中）几乎一切都就是这么回事。”|source=得知自己因饰演柯克·拉扎勒斯获得[[奥斯卡最佳男配角奖|奥斯卡最佳男配角奖]]提名后，小罗伯特·唐尼表示<ref name="USADowneyQuote">{{cite news | last = Wloszczyna | first = Susan | title = Downey digs Oscar adulation, but also knows it's fleeting | work = USA Today | date = 2009-02-03 | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/movies/news/2009-02-02-downey-oscar_N.htm | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2012-11-02 | accessdate = 2014-11-09 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121102091800/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/movies/news/2009-02-02-downey-oscar_N.htm}}</ref>。}}

2008年10月，派拉蒙电影公司开始为《热带惊雷》在年底的电影奖项角逐造势，并为唐尼宣传，希望他能获得[[奥斯卡最佳男配角奖|奥斯卡最佳男配角奖]]提名<ref name="DowneyBestSupport">{{cite news | last = Cieply | first = Michael | author2 = Brooks Barnes | url = http://www.nytimes.com/2008/10/28/movies/28stud.html?_r=0 | title = Studios Are Pushing Box Office Winners as Oscar Contenders | work = The New York Times | date = 2008-10-28 | accessdate = 2014-11-09 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141109154455/http://www.nytimes.com/2008/10/28/movies/28stud.html?_r=0 | archivedate = 2014-11-09 | publisher = The New York Times Company}}</ref>。2008年11月出版的《娱乐周刊》中认为，唐尼将与另外两人竞争这一奖项<ref name="DowneyEWSupport">{{cite journal|last=Karger |first=Dave |title=The Oscar Race |journal=Entertainment Weekly |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20237202,00.html |page=67 |issue=1019 |date=2008-11-07 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140922020537/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0%2C%2C20237202%2C00.html |archivedate=2014-09-22 |accessdate=2014-11-09 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。作为一种将戏中戏扩展到现实生活的方式，互联网上出现了至少两段“供您参考”的广告，宣传唐尼扮演的柯克·拉扎勒斯角逐最佳男配角奖，其中一场还包括《撒旦小径》中没有在伪预告片中出现的“镜头” 。派拉蒙影业还至少为唐尼的角色制作了一段打算作为早期“供您参考”视频的宣传广告<ref name="DowneyAdsLazarus">{{cite news | last = Wieselman | first = Jarett | url = http://blogs.nypost.com/popwrap/archives/2008/12/robert_downeys.html | title = Robert Downey's Creative Campaign | work = New York Post | date = 2008-12-09 | archivedate = 2009-06-13 | accessdate = 2009-06-13 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090613074407/http://blogs.nypost.com/popwrap/archives/2008/12/robert_downeys.html}}</ref>。2009年1月22日，[[美国电影艺术与科学学院|美国电影艺术与科学学院]]宣布唐尼获得男配角奖提名<ref name="DowneyJanNom">{{cite news | last = Serjeant | first = Jill | url = http://www.reuters.com/article/2009/01/22/us-oscars-ledger-sb-idINTRE50L3RU20090122 | title = No joke: Ledger earns posthumous Oscar nod | publisher = Reuters | date = 2009-01-22 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131005224621/http://www.reuters.com/article/2009/01/22/us-oscars-ledger-sb-idINTRE50L3RU20090122 | archivedate = 2013-10-05 | accessdate = 2013-10-05}}</ref>，但最终在[[第81届奥斯卡金像奖|第81届奥斯卡颁奖典礼]]上胜出的是出演《蝙蝠侠：黑暗骑士》的[[希斯·莱杰|希斯·莱杰]]<ref name="DowneyLedger">{{cite news|last=Germain |first=David |url=http://www.denverpost.com/ci_11762996 |title=Ledger's Joker triumphs at Academy Awards |work=Denver Post |date=2009-02-23 |accessdate=2014-11-09 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140922021629/http://www.denverpost.com/ci_11762996 |archivedate=2014-09-22 }}</ref>。

随着2008年底好莱坞年度电影颁奖季的来临，《热带惊雷》开始获得多个组织和团体的奖项及提名，首先是于2008年10月27日赢得第12届好莱坞电影节的“好莱坞年度喜剧奖”<ref name="HollyComAwa">{{cite web | url = http://www.hollywoodawards.com/winners/winners2008.html | title = Hollywood Awards Launches The Awards Season | date = 2008-10-28 | publisher = Hollywood Film Festival | accessdate = 2012-11-14 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121114190609/http://hollywoodawards.com/winners/winners2008.html | archivedate = 2012-11-14}}</ref><ref name="HollywoodComedyAward">{{cite news | last = Hammond | first = Pete | url = http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/season/2008/10/hollywood-lovef.html | title = Hollywood Lovefest launches season of giving | work = Los Angeles Times | date = 2008-10-28 | accessdate = 2009-01-07 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090107230438/http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/season/2008/10/hollywood-lovef.html | archivedate = 2009-01-07}}</ref>。影片在[[卫星奖|卫星奖]]角逐中获音乐剧及喜剧类最佳影片奖提名，唐尼也获得了最佳男配角奖提名<ref name="Satell2008Nom">{{cite web | url = http://www.pressacademy.com/satawards/awards2008.shtml | title = 2008 13th Annual Satellite Awards Nominees | date = 2008-10-28 | publisher = International Press Academy | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20111117163101/http://www.pressacademy.com/satawards/awards2008.shtml | archivedate = 2011-11-11 | accessdate = 2011-11-11 | deadurl = yes}}</ref>。[[广播影评人协会|广播影评人协会]]提名唐尼角逐最佳男配角奖，并授予《热带惊雷》[[评论家选择奖|评论家选择奖]]最佳喜剧电影奖<ref name="BFCA2008">{{cite web | url = http://www.bfca.org/ccawards/2008.php | title = The 14th Critics' Choice Awards Nominees | date = 2009-01-08 | publisher = Broadcast Film Critics Association | accessdate = 2013-01-21 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130121015848/http://www.bfca.org/ccawards/2008.php | archivedate = 2013-01-21}}</ref>。唐尼和克鲁斯都获[[好莱坞外国记者协会|好莱坞外国记者协会]]提名[[金球奖最佳电影男配角|金球奖最佳电影男配角奖]]<ref name="HFPA2008">{{cite web | url = http://www.goldenglobes.org/news/id/104 | title = Hollywood Foreign Press Association 2008 Golden Globe Awards Nominations for the Year Ended December 31, 2008 | date = 2008-12-11 | publisher = Hollywood Foreign Press Association | accessdate = 2010-11-11 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl  = https://web.archive.org/web/20101111004532/http://www.goldenglobes.org/news/id/104 | archivedate = 2010-11-11}}</ref>。[[波士顿影评人协会|波士顿影评人协会]]授予影片最佳群体演出奖<ref name="BostonEnsemble">{{cite news|last=Verniere |first=James |archivedate=2012-08-13 |accessdate=2012-08-13 |deadurl=yes |url=http://news.bostonherald.com/entertainment/movies/general/view/2008_12_15_%E2%80%98Slumdog_Millionaire__and_%E2%80%98WALL*E__wins_Boston_critics_Best_Picture_award/srvc=home&position=2 |title='Slumdog Millionaire' and 'WALL*E' win Boston critics Best Picture award |work=Boston Herald |date=2008-12-15 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120813051903/http://news.bostonherald.com/entertainment/movies/general/view/2008_12_15_%E2%80%98Slumdog_Millionaire__and_%E2%80%98WALL%2AE__wins_Boston_critics_Best_Picture_award/srvc%3Dhome%26position%3D2 }}</ref>。唐尼还获得了[[美国演员工会奖|美国演员工会]]和[[英国电影和电视艺术学院|英国电影和电视艺术学院]]的最佳男配角奖提名<ref name="DowneyBestSAG">{{cite news | last = Breznican | first = Anthony | accessdate = 2014-11-10 | deadurl = no | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/movies/movieawards/2008-12-18-sag-nominations_N.htm | title = Screen Actors Guild puts 'Doubt' into awards race | work = USA Today | date = 2008-12-18 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131206050155/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/movies/movieawards/2008-12-18-sag-nominations_N.htm | archivedate = 2013-12-06}}</ref><ref name="DowneyBestBAFTA">{{cite news | last = King | first = Susan | url = http://articles.latimes.com/2009/jan/16/entertainment/et-baftas16 | title = 'Benjamin Button' and 'Slumdog' lead BAFTAs | work = Los Angeles Times | date = 2009-01-16 | accessdate = 2014-11-10 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121024032751/http://articles.latimes.com/2009/jan/16/entertainment/et-baftas16 | archivedate = 2012-10-24}}</ref>。

