2008年11月18日，《热带惊雷》在美国发行{{lang|en|[[DVD|DVD]]}}和[[蓝光光盘|蓝光光盘]]，这时距电影在美加两国首映已经过了3个月，距院线放映周期结束也过了一星期<ref name="BOXMOJO" />。2009年1月26日，影片的家用媒体在[[英国|英国]]发行。其中的特别花絮包括电影未分级的导演剪辑版本、评论音轨（其中有一条是由斯蒂勒、唐尼和布莱克讲解，并且唐尼还是以林肯·奥西里斯的身份解说，意指拉扎勒斯一直保持着入戏状态直到{{lang|en|DVD}}评论音轨结束）、多段花絮内容、删除镜头和不同的结局，还有伪纪录片《疯狂的雨》<ref name="DVDAnnounced">{{cite news | last = Heldenfels | first = Rich | title = 'Tropic Thunder' rolls out extras: DVD of Ben Stiller film features commentary, mockumentary, outtakes | publisher = [http://www.ohio.com/ Ohio.com] | date = 2008-11-16 | archivedate = 2011-06-15 | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.ohio.com/entertainment/34538714.html | format = Registration required | accessdate = 2011-06-15 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110615134641/http://www.ohio.com/entertainment/34538714.html}}</ref><ref name="DVDHere">{{cite news | last = Conti | first = Garrett | title = New DVD releases include Tropic Thunder | work = Pittsburgh Tribune-Review | date = 2008-11-11 | accessdate = 2014-11-10 | deadurl = no | url = http://triblive.com//x/pittsburghtrib/ae/movies/s_599007.html#axzz3IfY73GbC | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141110124459/http://triblive.com//x/pittsburghtrib/ae/movies/s_599007.html | archivedate = 2014-11-10}}</ref><ref name="DowneyDVDCommentary">{{cite news | last = Lynch | first = Jason | title = Robert Downey Jr. Brings the Thunder | work = People | date = 2008-11-24 | url = http://libproxy.sdsu.edu/login?url=http://search.ebscohost.com.libproxy.sdsu.edu/login.aspx?direct=true&db=aph&AN=35275128&site=ehost-live | format = Registration required | accessdate = 2009-09-07 | archive-date = 2019-07-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190713000932/https://library.sdsu.edu/offcampus/login.php?url=http%3A%2F%2Fsearch.ebscohost.com.libproxy.sdsu.edu%2Flogin.aspx%3Fdirect%3Dtrue&db=aph&AN=35275128&site=ehost-live | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

电影的家用媒体发行第一周就登上了多个录像带排行榜，在尼尔森视频扫描第一警报销售排行榜和尼尔森蓝光光盘排行榜上都名列第2位，即便不计算蓝光光盘销售收入，进账也达到1906万4959美元<ref name="DVDSales">{{cite web | url = http://the-numbers.com/movie/Tropic-Thunder#tab=video-sales | title = Tropic Thunder — DVD Sales | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141101205558/http://www.the-numbers.com/movie/Tropic-Thunder#tab=video-sales | publisher = The Numbers | accessdate = 2014-11-10 | archivedate = 2014-11-01 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。出租市场方面，《热带惊雷》在《家用媒体杂志》的录像带出租排行榜上位居榜首<ref name="DVDCharts">{{cite news | last = Arnold | first = Thomas K. | title = "WALL-E" and "Thunder" top DVD charts | publisher = Reuters | date = 2008-11-27 | accessdate = 2014-11-10 | url = http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/11/27/centertainment-us-dvd-idCATRE4AQ29S20081127 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121113125437/http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/11/27/centertainment-us-dvd-idCATRE4AQ29S20081127 | archivedate = 2012-11-13}}</ref>。2008年影片的{{lang|en|DVD}}销售总收入达4227万1059美元，名列年度{{lang|en|DVD}}销售排行榜第28位<ref name="DVDSalesRank">{{cite web | accessdate = 2014-11-10 | url = http://www.the-numbers.com/home-market/dvd-sales/2008 | title = Top-Selling DVDs of 2008 | publisher = The Numbers | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141010094356/http://www.the-numbers.com/home-market/dvd-sales/2008 | archivedate = 2014-10-10 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。截至2009年9月，电影的{{lang|en|DVD}}一共售出了296.3万份，收入达4987万零248美元<ref name="DVDSales" />。

== 争议 ==
[[File:TropicThunderprotest.jpg|left]]
残疾人权利倡导人士对《热带惊魂》提出批评，梦工厂为此于8月4日撤掉了《笨蛋阿瓜》的网站，多个团体对片中描绘的智障形象提出质疑<ref name="SimpleJackPulled" />。梦工厂的发言人表示：“我们听到了他们的顾虑，我们也明白在断章取义的情况下，这个网站看起来对残疾人缺乏同情心理”<ref name="SimpleJackPulled" />。包括[[特殊奥林匹克运动会|特殊奥林匹克运动会]]和[[美国弧光会|美国弧光会]]在内的20多个残疾人维权组织结成联盟，抗议片中大量使用“白痴”一词<ref name="NYTBoycott" />。梦工厂提议在8月8日向这些团体放映本片，以期确定影片是否仍然会让他们感到冒犯<ref name="DreamWorksMeet">{{cite news | last = Cieply | first = Michael | title = Dreamworks to Meet With Disability Groups | work = The New York Times | date = 2008-08-05 | accessdate = 2014-11-10 | deadurl = no | publisher = The New York Times Company | url = http://www.nytimes.com/2008/08/05/arts/05arts-DREAMWORKSTO_BRF.html?_r=0 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141110131530/http://www.nytimes.com/2008/08/05/arts/05arts-DREAMWORKSTO_BRF.html?_r=0 | archivedate = 2014-11-10}}</ref><ref name="BusinessOffend">{{cite news | last = Lewis | first = Hilary | title = DreamWorks "Retard" Scandal Update: Disability-Rights Groups To Watch "Tropic Thunder", See If They Are Offended | publisher = [http://www.businesssheet.com/ The Business Insider] | date = 2008-08-07 | archivedate = 2012-07-30 | url = http://www.businessinsider.com/2008/8/dreamworks-retard-scandal-update-disability-rights-groups-to-watch-tropic-thunder-see-if-they-are-offended | accessdate = 2014-11-10 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120730100938/http://www.businessinsider.com/2008/8/dreamworks-retard-scandal-update-disability-rights-groups-to-watch-tropic-thunder-see-if-they-are-offended}}</ref>。这次放映之后推迟到了8月11日，和首映式是同一天<ref name="PostPoneScreen">{{cite news | last = Cieply | first = Michael | title = Groups Call for Boycott of 'Tropic Thunder' Film | work = The New York Times | url = http://www.nytimes.com/2008/08/12/business/media/12boycott.html | date = 2008-08-11 | publisher = The New York Times Company | accessdate = 2014-11-10 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090425030533/http://www.nytimes.com/2008/08/12/business/media/12boycott.html | archivedate = 2009-04-25}}</ref>。各团体派出代表观看了影片，这些代表认为自己受到了电影内容的冒犯，相应团体也就在电影的首映式举办地抗议<ref name="Mortified">{{cite news | last = Lewis | first = Hilary | title = Disability-Rights Groups See "Tropic Thunder", Mortified By "Retard" Jokes | publisher = [http://www.businesssheet.com/ The Business Insider] | date = 2008-08-11 | archivedate = 2013-06-19 | accessdate = 2014-11-10 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.businessinsider.com/2008/8/disability-rights-groups-agree-tropic-thunder-more-offensive-to-retards-than-other-groups | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130619221306/http://www.businessinsider.com/2008/8/disability-rights-groups-agree-tropic-thunder-more-offensive-to-retards-than-other-groups}}</ref><ref name="PremPick">{{cite news | last = Zeidler | first = Sue | title = Advocates for disabled to protest "Tropic Thunder" | publisher = Reuters | date = 2008-08-11 | archivedate = 2013-06-03 | url = http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/08/11/us-boycott-disability-idUSN1029346220080811 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130603034432/http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/08/11/us-boycott-disability-idUSN1029346220080811 | accessdate = 2014-11-10}}</ref>。特殊奥林匹克运动会主席[[蒂莫西·施莱佛|蒂莫西·施莱佛]]（{{lang|en|Timothy Shriver}}）表示：“这部分人群为了基本权利已经奋斗了太久，所以不得不争扎着与好莱坞对抗。我们是在表明立场，不会再接受这种仇恨言论”<ref name="ShrivOly">{{cite news | last = Lang | first = Derrick | title = Mental disability groups protest 'Tropic Thunder' | work = USA Today | date = 2008-08-12 | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/movies/news/2008-08-12-thunder-protest_N.htm | accessdate = 2014-11-10 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121102114220/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/movies/news/2008-08-12-thunder-protest_N.htm | archivedate = 2012-11-02}}</ref>。

包括残疾人权利倡导人士在内的一些观看过电影的人们指出，影片剧情中到处都有针对智障人士的攻击<ref name="PostPoneScreen" />。他们敦促人们不要去看这部电影，称影片贬低存在精神残疾人士的同时，还会助长霸凌行为<ref name="BullyingWicked">{{cite news | last = McCarthy | first = Jerry | title = Opinion: 'Tropic Thunder' movie is hurtful to many | publisher = ''Swampscott Reporter'' | url = http://www.wickedlocal.com/swampscott/news/lifestyle/columnists/x359568136/Opinion-Tropic-Thunder-movie-is-hurtful-to-many |date= 2008-09-04 | archivedate = 2013-07-30 | accessdate = 2013-07-30 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130730044837/http://www.wickedlocal.com/swampscott/news/lifestyle/columnists/x359568136/Opinion-Tropic-Thunder-movie-is-hurtful-to-many}}</ref>。斯蒂勒为自己的作品辩护，称“我们把电影放映过很多遍，这个问题直到很晚才浮现……在我看来，电影中的内容非常明确，只是在取笑那些试图通过严肃的角色去赢得电影奖项的演员”<ref name="StillerDefend">{{cite news | last = Netter | first = Sarah | coauthors = Chris Connelly and Arash Ghadishah | title = Ben Stiller: Taking Chances with "Tropic Thunder" | publisher = ABC News | date = 2008-08-13 | deadurl = no | url = http://abcnews.go.com/Nightline/story?id=5567544&page=1 | archivedate = 2014-10-26 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141026174421/http://abcnews.go.com/Nightline/story?id=5567544&page=1 | accessdate = 2014-10-26}}</ref>。编剧伊坦·柯亨认同斯蒂勒的观点：“一些人觉得这是在取笑残疾人，但我们实际上是在嘲笑那些把这些素材作为获奖资本的演员”<ref name="EtanQuote">{{cite news | last = Adler | first = Shawn | coauthors = Yasmine Richard and Josh Horowitz | title = 'Tropic Thunder' Director/Star Ben Stiller Says Disability Advocates' Planned Boycott Is Unwarranted | publisher = MTV | deadurl = no | url = http://www.mtv.com/news/1592544/tropic-thunder-directorstar-ben-stiller-says-disability-advocates-planned-boycott-is-unwarranted/ | archivedate = 2014-11-10 | accessdate = 2014-11-10 | date = 2008-08-11 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141110140427/http://www.mtv.com/news/1592544/tropic-thunder-directorstar-ben-stiller-says-disability-advocates-planned-boycott-is-unwarranted/}}</ref>。他还进一步列举了多位以扮演弱智或患[[自闭症|自闭症]]角色的演员，称电影就是在取笑他们，如《[[雨人|雨人]]》中的[[达斯汀·霍夫曼|达斯汀·霍夫曼]]、《阿甘正传》中的[[汤姆·汉克斯|汤姆·汉克斯]]、《[[真情电波|真情电波]]》中的[[小库珀·古丁|小库珀·古丁]]和《[[我是山姆|我是山姆]]》中的[[西恩·潘|西恩·潘]]<ref name="EtanQuote" />。梦工厂的发言人没有直接就这些批评做出回应，而是称“《热带惊雷》……是一部讽刺好莱坞及其过分行为的{{lang|en|R}}级喜剧电影，为了体现这一立场，其中展现了身穿荒谬处境人物失当和夸张的所做所为”<ref name="NYTBoycott" />。影片的宣传广告做了调整，但电影本身的内容并没有因这些抗议活动而出现变化<ref name="NYTBoycott" /><ref name="PremPick" />。作为对这些争议的回应，{{lang|en|DVD}}中的导演剪辑版在特别花絮中增加了公益广告，建议观众不要使用“白痴”一词，不过蓝光光盘版本中没有这样的内容<ref name="DVDPSA">{{cite news | last = Shriver | first = Maria | title = The 'R-word' is no joke | work = Los Angeles Times | accessdate = 2014-11-10 | deadurl = no | url = http://articles.latimes.com/2008/aug/22/news/OE-SHRIVER22 | date = 2008-08-22 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121024134554/http://articles.latimes.com/2008/aug/22/news/OE-SHRIVER22 | archivedate = 2012-10-24}}</ref>。

