2008年8月5日，《热带惊雷》的[[电影配乐|配乐]]唱片面世，这时距影片在院线上映还有一星期。配乐由西奥多·沙皮洛作曲，好莱坞演播室交响乐团演奏。{{lang|en|[[Allmusic|Allmusic]]}}网站的威廉·鲁尔曼（{{lang|en|William Ruhlmann}}）给予乐曲正面评价，称这是“……由内部人士执笔，对好莱坞动作电影音乐史深切而明显的讽刺”<ref name="TTScore">{{cite web | last = Ruhlmann | first = William | archivedate = 2012-10-24 | accessdate = 2014-11-10 | url = http://www.allmusic.com/album/tropic-thunder-original-motion-picture-score-mw0000796299 | title = Tropic Thunder (Score) Review | work = allmusic | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121024134554/http://articles.latimes.com/2008/aug/22/news/OE-SHRIVER22}}</ref>。{{lang|en|SoundtrackNet}}网站的托马斯·辛普森（{{lang|en|Thomas Simpson}}）则称其“……融搞笑、严肃、[[摇滚乐|摇滚]]和伟大的音乐于一体”<ref name="SNetScore">{{cite web | last = Simpson | first = Thomas | url = http://www.soundtrack.net/album/tropic-thunder-score/ | title = Tropic Thunder (score) | publisher = SoundtrackNet | date = 2008-08-12 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141110142515/http://www.soundtrack.net/album/tropic-thunder-score/ | archivedate = 2014-11-10 | accessdate = 2014-11-10 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。

电影中有5首歌曲没有包含在原声带里，分别是[[悄声暴动合唱团|悄声暴动合唱团]]的“{{lang|en|Cum On Feel the Noize}}”、[[滚石乐队|滚石乐队]]的“{{lang|en|Sympathy for the Devil}}”、[[水牛春田合唱团|水牛春田合唱团]]的“{{lang|en|For What It's Worth}}”、[[佛罗·里达|佛罗·里达]]和{{lang|en|[[T-Pain|T-Pain]]}}的“{{lang|en|Low}}”以及[[卢达克里斯|卢达克里斯]]的“{{lang|en|Get Back}}”。原声带中收录了[[诱惑合唱团|诱惑合唱团]]、[[汉默|汉默]]（{{lang|en|MC Hammer}}）、[[克里登斯清水复兴合唱团|克里登斯清水复兴合唱团]]、[[埃德温·斯塔尔|埃德温·斯塔尔]]（{{lang|en|Edwin Starr}}）及其他艺术家的作品。[[水晶疗法乐团|水晶疗法乐团]]的单曲“{{lang|en|Name of the Game}}”由瑞安·帕特里克·马金（{{lang|en|Ryan Patrick Maginn}}，又名{{lang|en|Ryu}}）演绎，对音乐做了[[重混|重混]]录制。<ref name="TTSoundtrack">{{cite web | url = http://www.ign.com/articles/2008/07/18/tropic-thunder-drops-the-bomb | author = IGN Music | title = Tropic Thunder Drops The Bomb | publisher = IGN | date = 2009-09-07 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121025231709/http://www.ign.com/articles/2008/07/18/tropic-thunder-drops-the-bomb | archivedate = 2012-10-25 | accessdate = 2012-10-25}}</ref>这张唱片一经发行就在《[[告示牌_(杂志)|告示牌]]》畅销原声带唱片榜上名列第20位，并且最高在《告示牌》的畅销独立唱片榜上名列第39位<ref name="SoundtrackBillboard">{{cite news | title = Top Independent | work = Billboard | date = 2008-09-06 | url = http://libproxy.sdsu.edu/login?url=http://search.ebscohost.com.libproxy.sdsu.edu/login.aspx?direct=true&db=aph&AN=34216159&site=ehost-live | accessdate = 2010-11-07 | archive-date = 2019-07-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190713000932/https://library.sdsu.edu/offcampus/login.php?url=http%3A%2F%2Fsearch.ebscohost.com.libproxy.sdsu.edu%2Flogin.aspx%3Fdirect%3Dtrue&db=aph&AN=34216159&site=ehost-live | dead-url = no }}</ref>。{{lang|en|Allmusic}}网站的詹姆斯·克里斯托弗·蒙哥（{{lang|en|James Christopher Monger}}）将本片的音乐与《野战排》、《全金属外壳》和《阿甘正传》相比，觉得乐曲虽然“……有趣，但听起来略有些20世纪70年代末那种老式的{{lang|en|K-Tel}}音乐唱片汇编在一起，然后再加上一些来自未来的加量曲目混合起来的感觉”<ref name="AllmusicReview">{{cite web | last = Monger | first = James Christopher | url = http://www.allmusic.com/album/tropic-thunder-original-soundtrack-mw0000792940 | title = Tropic Thunder (Original Soundtrack) 